	  clock_control_set_rate() / _configure() (our upstream clockctrl has only
	  .on/.off/.get_rate).  The bit-clock divider is therefore NOT programmed
	  from the requested sample rate -- exact SCLK is BENCH-UNVERIFIED until the
	  clockctrl gains a real .set_rate for the I2Sx_CTRL divider.

	  ADR 0017 Tier-2 (a genuine fork-driver copy): INTERIM.  Retires onto the
	  opt-in fork once bench-verified.  Task #21.  Driver: zephyr/drivers/i2s/i2s_dw.c.

